  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1680184705\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Having lost your tribe, you as the sole survivor, find yourself in an era of deadly danger and exciting adventures. You have to build yourself a shelter, make weapons, protect yourself from wild animals, and prove that you are not a prey, but a predator.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/d82ff7cd2c02ebc1680606c22e282a5f.poster.avif?t=1680184705\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/d82ff7cd2c02ebc1680606c22e282a5f.webm?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/d82ff7cd2c02ebc1680606c22e282a5f.mp4?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build your shelter, craft tools, weapons, collect resources in different biomes to create whatever you need, and conquer the world as you see it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features :</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Implemented construction, craft, fishing, farming, hunting, cooking.<br></li><li>Random open world with 5 biomes<br></li><li>Lots of buildings, tools, weapons and resources.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/008862b2809cddeeb61c670d13414def.poster.avif?t=1680184705\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/008862b2809cddeeb61c670d13414def.webm?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/008862b2809cddeeb61c670d13414def.mp4?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In addition, there are many more different tasks and tests waiting for you.<br><br><br><br>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1680184705\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Having lost your tribe, you as the sole survivor, find yourself in an era of deadly danger and exciting adventures. You have to build yourself a shelter, make weapons, protect yourself from wild animals, and prove that you are not a prey, but a predator.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/d82ff7cd2c02ebc1680606c22e282a5f.poster.avif?t=1680184705\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/d82ff7cd2c02ebc1680606c22e282a5f.webm?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/d82ff7cd2c02ebc1680606c22e282a5f.mp4?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build your shelter, craft tools, weapons, collect resources in different biomes to create whatever you need, and conquer the world as you see it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features :</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Implemented construction, craft, fishing, farming, hunting, cooking.<br></li><li>Random open world with 5 biomes<br></li><li>Lots of buildings, tools, weapons and resources.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/008862b2809cddeeb61c670d13414def.poster.avif?t=1680184705\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/008862b2809cddeeb61c670d13414def.webm?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218480/extras/008862b2809cddeeb61c670d13414def.mp4?t=1680184705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In addition, there are many more different tasks and tests waiting for you.<br><br><br><br>",
